<h1>AlphabetSoup Help</h1>

<br>This game uses the alphabet to exercise and stretch your brain.
<br>
<br>Each puzzle will be letters placed in random positions on the board.
<br>
<br>Memorize the positions of the letters in the layout.
<br>
<br>When you click READY, the letters will disappear, but the boxes that held them will remain.
<br>
<br>Click on the boxes in alphabetical order to recreate the puzzle.
<br>
<br>If you make a mistake, you will be prompted to try again.
